    <a title="Alexander" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8539089-alexander"><img alt="Alexander" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1471881162p2/8539089.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1932725739?book_show_action=true">Mar 05, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alexander" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alexander" href="/user/show/8539089-alexander">Alexander</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1932725739" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9405856148579979338">Tiger and the Robot was a fun, fast-paced adventure, filled with the sorts of unexpected twists and turns that make for a good detective story. The author&apos;s knowledge of both ships and programming shines through in the texture of those scenes.</span>
  <span id="freeText9405856148579979338" style="display:none">Tiger and the Robot was a fun, fast-paced adventure, filled with the sorts of unexpected twists and turns that make for a good detective story. The author's knowledge of both ships and programming shines through in the texture of those scenes.</span>
  <a data-text-id="9405856148579979338" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
