<div id="review_1962556852" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1962556852" />
    <a title="Patrick Chiu" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/66617461-patrick-chiu"><img alt="Patrick Chiu" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1491374711p2/66617461.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1962556852?book_show_action=true">Apr 04, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Patrick Chiu" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Patrick Chiu" href="/user/show/66617461-patrick-chiu">Patrick Chiu</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1962556852" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6293384828552483240">This adventure novel had me hooked after each chapter, leaving me wondering how the kidnapping mystery would unfold. It was filled with suspense and thrill as Chan and Saga worked together to face unexpected challenges along the way. The personality of characters and descriptive text played a movie in my head as a read on. This is an easy read that I recommend and I look forward to more books from Grahame Shannon!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


